name: RENT A RABBIT WORKSHOP DEPOSIT
description:
Go to this link for more info:
http://ambikaboutique.bigcartel.com/rent-a-rabbit

What is Rent-A-Rabbit?

Really want a pet, but you are not allowed to have one in your apartment? Always wanted to learn how to spin and crochet and make your own handmade winter wear? This is the best of both worlds. Now, you can rent an exotic angora rabbit and come visit it quarterly in upstate NY in the catskill mountains. You'll learn the whole process from fiber to finished garment over the course of a year by joining other like minded folks every three months for workshops. The following winter the wool from your very own rabbit will be keeping you super warm. One rabbit makes up to 8 hats per year!

name: English Angora Bunnies make great pets!
description:
Not only do they make great pets, but they give back too. You can make up to 8 hats per year from their silky fiber! In this age of fast fashion, there is nothing more satisfying than keeping warm and knowing exactly where your hat came from! Your very own happy bunny! 

Having a bunny opens you to an amazing world of fiber arts, where you can learn to spin and crochet their wool. Giving someone a hand spun, hand crochet bunny hat, as a gift, is the greatest reward!

Put your order in now to reserve one of these fluffy little cuties. Summer litters coming soon. Join our workshops and learn how to create beautiful handspun garments from their fiber!

They can also be house trained like cats and dogs! 
http://www.angorarabbit.com/angora/angora-guide/index.htm
